summary.overview: The conversation is a loan application verification call where the AI asks the user to confirm personal details. The user complies with all requests, having initially asked the AI to speak quickly.
summary.user_tone: Initially urgent and direct, then cooperative and straightforward.

conversation.speaker: ai
